<h2>What is partner consent?</h2>
<p>We require your partner's consent in order to process any information you provide to us on behalf of your partner. To give this consent follow the steps below.</p>

<h2>Steps to provide consent:</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Download the <a>partner consent form</a>.</li>
  <li>Print and complete the form and have it signed by your partner.</li>
  <li>Scan or photograph the completed form and upload below.</li>
</ol>

<hr>
<div class="container container--8-column">
